text: "Supersonic Rocket Ship" is a 1972 song by British band The Kinks and was taken from their eleventh studio album Everybody's in Show-Biz. It went to number 16 in the United Kingdom and number 111 in the United States. It was a minor hit along with Celluloid Heroes. == References == Category:1972 songs Category:The Kinks songs
title: Supersonic Rocket Ship
